name: Wardens of the Cosmos
description: Seemingly appearing out of thin air, the Wardens of the Cosmos arenâ€™t even sure where they themselves are from. Without a known heritage to lean on, they identify as children of the cosmos. They also owe a debt of gratitude to the Groodu for deliverance in their time of need. Now armed with knowledge of the stars, moons, and tides, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
